{"tid":1803722,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中電港燈引入世界各地天然氣發電 減少內地壟斷","createTime":"2019-12-30T12:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T05:22:07.000Z","uid":216555,"like":878,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"0a793f2b2059f8f45fc69c8f0cd9817bf4de1f4d","tid":1803722,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:00:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NVUuWv8VViA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNVUuWv8VViA&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=c043b0b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NVUuWv8VViA</a><br />\n<br />\n到時可以新加坡引入先進海水淨化技術令香港自給自足<br />\n<br />\n我寧願俾多啲電費都唔要依靠大陸 好彩誠哥目標長遠天然氣一早買其他國家 都好過中電天然氣一直比大陸壟斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家中電同港燈合資起緊個天然氣接收站可以全世界買氣 不過仲要幾年先ok <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而港燈向<span style=\"color: red;\">澳洲和卡塔爾</span>購買液化天然氣，用船運至從廣東液化天然氣接收站，經過海底喉管將天然氣輸送至南丫島發電廠。2014年之前，中電採購天然氣價錢較港燈便宜，但2014年國際氣價大幅下跌，港燈更換新買氣合約，其後5年平均氣價較中電便宜36.9%（見表）。若中電跟隨港燈採購價，5年間可節省120億元買氣成本，等於平均每個用戶可節省4,580元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191206/60324758\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191206%2F60324758&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=3348cef5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191206%2F60324758&h=e708909c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191206/60324758</a>"},{"pid":"41e9732c0a0559fb42c645482b572ab075256258","tid":1803722,"uid":305536,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=3e0f7ffd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=65f92fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要33000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=1089bb90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">簽完share去tg</span></span>"},{"pid":"4325f564a799a9012f837fc70358cd35eb50f4c5","tid":1803722,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:05:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2df2327bf0432506dc2d9953284dfb3a003b34c6","tid":1803722,"uid":58164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1693a6b57c432dfdd05ea60d047d0e2229c377","tid":1803722,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T12:10:56.000Z","msg":